cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to 5 (invalid value, valid range 0-3) will cause configuration validation failure in the RACH configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為 5（無效值，有效範圍 0-3）會在 RACH 配置中導致配置驗證失敗。
